name: "Buraya Bakarlar"
description: "Buraya Bakarlar" sentence means "They look here" in Turkish. When I first moved to the city where I live now, I saw a billboard with only an eye picture and this sentence written over it. It instantly took me back to my childhood memories where my granny looked after me. Now it's time for me to look after her. Age is just a concept, and time is limitless...
